title: Don't Let Your Ego Hurt Your Effectiveness, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO64
description: If you think humility has nothing to do with success, you're wrong. People who think they know everything and can do everything very seldom accomplish anything. Winning in business and life requires the ability to know what you know and what you don't know, and the commitment to surround yourself with people who help you maximize your strengths and minimize your weaknesses.
